race.description: Sportsbet Nobody Does It Easier F&M Maiden Plate
race.comment: MALDIVICA (10) resumed from a long break with a strong on pace fourth at the provincials. Fitter again and off the low draw looks hard to run down. QUEEN CALANTHE (7) is a long time maiden but went close fresh over 1000m at Mildura, beaten half a length. This no tougher and fitter again. Tricky gate but will give a sight. BLABBER MOUTH (8) is the big watch in the race. Filly by All Too Hard out of Canyoukeepasecret who is at the races for the first time. Fitter for three trials, two this time in. Top yard and very wary if heavily bet. BRIMARVI ROSEMARIE (3) was safely held fresh at the provincials but did get going late. Extra trip a plus and has the blinkers added. BENDING AWAY (2) is well weighted fresh and can run a race at odds.
